OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773450175
OL,3,CPublic to vote on artists shortlisted
OL,4,Cto create work from Sycamore Gap tree
OL,5,Cwood
OL,7,FThe public is being invited to vote on
OL,8,Fwhich of six shortlisted artists
OL,9,Fshould create an artwork from the wood
OL,10,Fof the illegally felled Sycamore Gap
OL,11,Ftree.
OL,13,FIn September, the National Trust
OL,14,Fcalled on artists, organisations and
OL,15,Fcreative agencies across the country
OL,16,Fto present ideas for a "nationally
OL,17,Fimportant" commission that helps shape
OL,18,Fthe tree's next chapter by using half
OL,19,Fof its timber.
OL,26,@xD@XOUyD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
