OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773450175
OL,3,CPublic to vote on artists shortlisted
OL,4,Cto create work from Sycamore Gap tree
OL,5,Cwood
OL,7,FThe charity unveiled the finalists on
OL,8,FSaturday at the same time as the
OL,9,Fpublic ballot opens, with voting
OL,10,Frunning until March 28.
OL,12,FPeople will be able to select from the
OL,13,Fsix different visions for how the
OL,14,Ftree's story, symbolism and memory can
OL,15,Flive on for future generations.
OL,17,FThe public's input will contribute to
OL,18,F30% of the final decision, while
OL,19,Fscores from a judging panel made up of
OL,20,Fnature and art experts will make up
OL,21,F70%.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773450175
OL,3,CPublic to vote on artists shortlisted
OL,4,Cto create work from Sycamore Gap tree
OL,5,Cwood
OL,7,FIt comes more than two years after
OL,8,FDaniel Graham and Adam Carruthers,
OL,9,Ffrom Cumbria, travelled to Hadrian's
OL,10,FWall in Northumberland during Storm
OL,11,FAgnes in 2023 to cut down the world-
OL,12,Ffamous tree, which is thought to have
OL,13,Fbeen planted in the late 1880s.
OL,15,FThe act of vandalism sparked national
OL,16,Foutrage and an outpouring of grief for
OL,17,Fthe widely loved landmark.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773450175
OL,3,CPublic to vote on artists shortlisted
OL,4,Cto create work from Sycamore Gap tree
OL,5,Cwood
OL,7,FAnnie Reilly, National Trust public
OL,8,Fengagement director and chairwoman of
OL,9,Fthe judging panel, said: "Over the
OL,10,Fpast two years, we've heard
OL,11,Fextraordinary stories about what the
OL,12,FSycamore Gap tree meant to people `
OL,13,Ffrom moments of celebration and
OL,14,Fmilestones to quiet memories of loss,
OL,15,Fconnection and reflection.
OL,17,F"It became more than a tree; it became
OL,18,Fpart of the emotional landscape of the
OL,19,Fnation."
OL,26,@qD@ZOUyD@AOU{D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
