PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773450175
OL,3,CPublic to vote on artists shortlisted
OL,4,Cto create work from Sycamore Gap tree
OL,5,Cwood
OL,7,FMs Reilly said the vote will give the
OL,8,Fpublic the opportunity to "help share
OL,9,Fthe ongoing story".
OL,11,F"Each of the six proposals honours the
OL,12,Ftree in a different way, and we want
OL,13,Fpeople to choose the idea that
OL,14,Fcaptures what the Sycamore Gap tree
OL,15,Fmeant to them," she said.
OL,17,FShortlisted proposals include ideas
OL,18,Fthat transform the Sycamore Gap tree
OL,19,Fwood into new artworks and sculptural
OL,20,Finstallations.
OL,26,@pD@[OUqD@RO]sD@AOUwD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
