SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773450175
OL,3,CPublic to vote on artists shortlisted
OL,4,Cto create work from Sycamore Gap tree
OL,5,Cwood
OL,7,FAlso put forward are nationwide
OL,8,Fparticipatory projects that gather
OL,9,Fpersonal stories, distribute symbolic
OL,10,Fcarved seeds, build platforms for
OL,11,Fconversations about climate or bring
OL,12,Fcommunities together in song and
OL,13,Fremembrance.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
