PN,30207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773450175
OL,3,CPublic to vote on artists shortlisted
OL,4,Cto create work from Sycamore Gap tree
OL,5,Cwood
OL,7,FThe six artists or collaborations are
OL,8,FAlex Hartley and Tom James, based in
OL,9,FDevon and London, Helix Arts x George
OL,10,FKing Architects, based in the North
OL,11,FEast, Mary Dalton, based in Hampshire,
OL,12,Fnon zero one, based in London, Sam
OL,13,FWilliams Studio, based in Sussex, and
OL,14,FTrigger, based in Bristol.
OL,16,FThe wood is now ready for artists to
OL,17,Fwork with after being stored to season
OL,18,Fover the past 28 months.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
