PN,30208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773450175
OL,3,CPublic to vote on artists shortlisted
OL,4,Cto create work from Sycamore Gap tree
OL,5,Cwood
OL,7,FThe winner will be announced later in
OL,8,Fthe spring and the final artwork is
OL,9,Fexpected to be completed by 2028.
OL,11,FThe initiative comes as part of a
OL,12,Fwider public engagement programme
OL,13,Fresponding to the tree's felling,
OL,14,Fsupported by Northumberland National
OL,15,FPark Authority (NNPA), Historic
OL,16,FEngland, the Hadrian's Wall
OL,17,FPartnership and the National Trust.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
