PN,30209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773450175
OL,3,CPublic to vote on artists shortlisted
OL,4,Cto create work from Sycamore Gap tree
OL,5,Cwood
OL,7,FSo far, the main section of the tree's
OL,8,Ftrunk has been installed at the
OL,9,Fgateway to Northumberland National
OL,10,FPark, where the tree once stood.
OL,12,FHeartwood prints from a cross-section
OL,13,Fof the trunk created by printmaker
OL,14,FShona Branigan are now on display at
OL,15,FSeaton Delaval Hall in Northumberland.
OL,17,FAnd UK communities were invited to
OL,18,Fapply for one of the 49 saplings grown
OL,19,Ffrom seeds rescued from the original
OL,20,Ftree and they have now been planted
OL,21,Facross the country.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
